Carino is a platform for building vehicles, remotely controlled via wifi.
It's main goals are:
 * tend to be as open as possible, from the the software to the hardware (but
   see note 1.)
 * be an educative platform, with a documentation on how to build a vehicle from
   the ground up, with various levels of reading so that the target audience can
   be as large as possible
 * provide completely finished, with an industry level quality
 * bring tons of fun to everyone, starting with me :)

